The paper deals with a question answering task using multiple documents as input, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories in computer science, including Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Among these, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely categories as they directly relate to the task of reading comprehension and document retrieval.
